OL,3,CFears of a bird flu outbreak as dozens
OL,4,Cof swans found dead in London Docklands
OL,6,FDozens of swans have been found dead
OL,7,Fin east London, prompting fears of a
OL,8,Fbird flu outbreak.
OL,10,FMillwall Dock is home to around 100 of
OL,11,Fthe birds but more than 30 have died
OL,12,Fin the last few days.
OL,14,FSwan Sanctuary volunteer Andy Miller
OL,15,Ftold ITV News London he had never seen
OL,16,Fanything like it.
OL,18,FHe said: "We've had other outbreaks of
OL,19,Fillnesses, bird flu, but this has
OL,20,Ftaken more than 30 so far.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/6
