CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1772041214
OL,3,CFears of a bird flu outbreak as dozens
OL,4,Cof swans found dead in London Docklands
OL,6,F"And the worst thing is that it tends
OL,7,Fto be the young ones, the cygnets,
OL,8,Fthat seem to be being hit worst of all
OL,9,F... and so far there's no prospect
OL,10,Fthat it's going to stop."
OL,12,FPassersby at the Docklands described
OL,13,Fthe scene as "very upsetting". One
OL,14,Fsaid: "I've seen about 15 swans
OL,15,Fliterally just die in front of me.
OL,16,FThey just get out of water, sit there,
OL,17,Ftheir heads go down, and within 10
OL,18,Fminutes, they're dead."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
