OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1772041214
OL,3,CFears of a bird flu outbreak as dozens
OL,4,Cof swans found dead in London Docklands
OL,6,FAnother added: "A lot of kids actually
OL,7,Fcome around here to see the swans,
OL,8,Ffeed the swans, and now they're seeing
OL,9,Fjust dead swans that's popping up."
OL,11,FMr Miller said his team is awaiting
OL,12,Ftest results from the Department for
OL,13,FEnvironment, Food & Rural Affairs
OL,14,F(DEFRA) to confirm the cause of death.
OL,16,FThe South Essex Wildlife Hospital has
OL,17,Fbeen receiving animals with suspected
OL,18,Fbird flu at their centre.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/6
