OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1772041214
OL,3,CFears of a bird flu outbreak as dozens
OL,4,Cof swans found dead in London Docklands
OL,6,FHead vet Tom Linsel said birds are
OL,7,Fbeing checked in the car park, with
OL,8,Fstaff wearing PPE, to avoid an
OL,9,Foutbreak at the centre.
OL,11,FHe said: "The birds will get checked.
OL,12,FIf we're suspecting there is a bird
OL,13,Fflu, even the minor, minor behavioural
OL,14,Fthings or any anatomical problems or
OL,15,Fanything, then unfortunately we have
OL,16,Fto put to sleep the bird."
OL,18,FIf vets are unsure, birds may be
OL,19,Fquarantined for seven days to see if
OL,20,Fsymptoms appear. Mr Linsel added: "We
OL,21,Fhave to be vigilant".
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/6
