OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1772041214
OL,3,CFears of a bird flu outbreak as dozens
OL,4,Cof swans found dead in London Docklands
OL,6,FSymptoms of bird flu include lethargy,
OL,7,Fa bird not being able to keep its head
OL,8,Fupright, looking generally unwell, and
OL,9,Fhaving flickering or glazed eyes.
OL,11,FMembers of the public have been urged
OL,12,Fnot to get too close.
OL,14,FA spokesperson from the Animal and
OL,15,FPlant Health Agency at DEFRA said: "We
OL,16,Fare aware of a number of swan deaths
OL,17,Faround West India and Millwall docks,
OL,18,Fand are investigating this as part of
OL,19,FAPHA's dead wild bird surveillance
OL,20,Fscheme"
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/6
