CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1772041214
OL,3,CFears of a bird flu outbreak as dozens
OL,4,Cof swans found dead in London Docklands
OL,6,F"Members of the public are advised to
OL,7,Fnot touch or pick up any dead or
OL,8,Fvisibly sick birds that they find and
OL,9,Fshould wash their hands thoroughly
OL,10,Fwith soap and water if they touch wild
OL,11,Fbird faeces or feathers or after
OL,12,Ffeeding wild birds."
